MPM 2020 mentions the “affaire Lunghi” in which three people have been convicted in 2019. Another recent court case involves a businessman who brought charges of defamation in three countries against a journalist of the daily Luxemburger Wort as well as its editor-in-chief and director for publishing an article critically covering his business activities. Charges were dropped in Luxembourg in August 2019.

                     

                  
 

                     
   
